    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《NO LAW》是一款剧情丰富的黑色电影风格第一人称赛博游戏，故事背景设定在一座霓虹闪烁却又污秽不堪的港口城市。这里充斥着罪恶而非法律，大多数人都被债务压得抬不起头，更会在某个转角被黑暗抹去存在。在欲望港中探索，夺回属于你的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5440f5f9e378f5794a03e94b90371917.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5440f5f9e378f5794a03e94b90371917.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5440f5f9e378f5794a03e94b90371917.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《NO LAW》中，你将扮演老兵格雷·哈克。他久经沙场，又深谙欲望港的生存法则。在最后一次出任务时，哈克身负重伤，几乎丢了性命，于是决定彻底告别军旅生涯，改而追寻平静的生活。然而，即使他已不再主动招惹麻烦，在某个宿命之日，麻烦还是找上了门来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/8418880835d2f816c297db397d531d3e.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/8418880835d2f816c297db397d531d3e.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/8418880835d2f816c297db397d531d3e.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >影响深远的玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便在这座无法无天的城市里，你的行动仍然会带来对应的后果。在扮演哈克的旅途中，你会遇到许多个性鲜明的人物，他们可能是朋友，也可能是敌人。无论你是伸出手去拯救落难同伴，还是让躲在巷子里的粗鄙鼠辈彻底闭嘴，你的选择都会留下痕迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5227c2880697152fe27bd0247c9e05a9.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5227c2880697152fe27bd0247c9e05a9.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/5227c2880697152fe27bd0247c9e05a9.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索欲望港</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欲望港是一座颓废的赛博工业城市，这里面朝大海，背傍峭壁，草木葱茏，鱼龙混杂，各色人等个性张扬。作为进出口贸易枢纽，三教九流都汇聚于此，想要追逐自己最疯狂的梦想。这座港口没有禁区，整座城市都是你的游乐场。就把道德留在城市之外吧——上到刺破雾霭的摩天楼顶，下至令人窒息的漆黑深巷，抛开一切束缚，尽情探索这座垂直奇观。但请谨慎选择前路：当一座城市没有了法律约束，就会有许多人开始自行伸张“正义”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/76d86fbe8eab985a8f291681aa6e57b7.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/76d86fbe8eab985a8f291681aa6e57b7.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/76d86fbe8eab985a8f291681aa6e57b7.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心游玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是会运用格雷的战术素养潜伏于阴影之中，还是放任他被失控的怒火驾驭，拿起枪直接冲锋？无论你更偏爱谋定后动，还是沉醉于破坏一切，都请务必抽出时间，查看琳琅满目的丰富的军事升级装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/f20ea5af132e4f8a5c9acb67b6023704.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/f20ea5af132e4f8a5c9acb67b6023704.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/f20ea5af132e4f8a5c9acb67b6023704.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/2b8ea854330786785eec3f4072b453a6.poster.avif?t=1765815627\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/2b8ea854330786785eec3f4072b453a6.webm?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161710/extras/2b8ea854330786785eec3f4072b453a6.mp4?t=1765815627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
